Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\bord0\c&HAF9E86&\pos(1081,657)}#发疯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs19\bord0\c&HA4A4A5&\pos(598,671)}赞
